## Usage Patterns

### Showcase

```tsx
() => {
  const [focused, setFocused] = useState(false);

  return (
    <>
      <ClickAwayListener onClickAway={() => setFocused(false)}>
        {(setRefNode) => (
          <Button innerRef={setRefNode} onClick={() => setFocused(true)}>
            Test focus
          </Button>
        )}
      </ClickAwayListener>
      <div>
        {focused === true ? 'Focused on button' : 'Focused on document'}
      </div>
    </>
  );
}
```

